subSubSection.paragraph:
Vermiform embryos (
Figs 12f
, 
13f, g
).

Full-grown vermiform embryos range length 105–230 µm and width 37–69µm. Peripheral cell number 32–38 (
Table 3
); trunk cells arranged in opposed pairs. Anterior end of calotte rounded. Axial cell rounded anteriorly, extending to propolar cells. Anterior abortive axial cell present (
Fig. 12f
). Axial cell of full-grown embryos with up to 36 agametes.
